reflect-shot = Рикошет!
# #Misfits Change Add: Descriptive ricochet message for sub-5.56mm rounds bouncing off power armor / shields.
reflect-shot-small-caliber = { $bullet } { $shooter } не пробил { $target } и отрикошетил!
# #Misfits Change Add: Glancing-blow message for rifle rounds deflecting off power armor plate at a low angle.
reflect-shot-medium-caliber = { $bullet } { $shooter } отлетела от силовой брони { $target }!
reflect-unknown-shooter = Кто-то